narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: The course was an excellent occasion to know better foundamental literature and to discuss foundamental questions

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The course is very broad and I think it was an essential piece of the puzzle for my instruction. I think that, given the so broad range of topics, it is unlikley that any student could have already a knowledge of all the topics discussed in the seminar. I would suggest to incorporate brief lectures regarding the general hypothesis sorrounding the general questions discussed in class.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes I think it is a course that everyone should take, in order to improve skills in discussing hypothesis
